characters.name: Lucie
characters.description: Lucie is a diverse contender who knows which brew makes you choke, heal or flee in fear. The arena has become her new playground for wild experiments.

battlerites.name: Weakening Toxin
battlerites.description: {2}Toxic{-} reduces incoming healing by {healingmodifier} and outgoing damage by {damagemodifier}.

battlerites.name: Vampiric Toxin
battlerites.description: {2}Toxic{-} heals you for {healing} health over {duration}.

battlerites.name: Stimulant
battlerites.description: ^2Revitalize^- increases damage output by {damagemodifier}.

battlerites.name: Companion Potion
battlerites.description: {2}Healing Potion{-} heals other allies for {bonusheal} bonus health.

battlerites.name: Alacrity
battlerites.description: ^2Barrier^- increases movement speed by {hastefactor}.

battlerites.name: Blast Shield
battlerites.description: Applying {2}Barrier{-} causes a shockwave, dealing {damage} damage to nearby enemies and knocking them back.

battlerites.name: Siege Barrier
battlerites.description: {2}Barrier{-} absorbs {shieldvalue} bonus damage and duration increases by {duration}.

battlerites.name: Adhesive Component
battlerites.description: {2}Clarity Potion{-} inflicts {slowpercent} {2}Snare{-} for {slowduration}.

battlerites.name: Potency
battlerites.description: ^2Clarity Potion^- heals {healing} health when removing a debuff and deals {damage} damage when removing a buff.

battlerites.name: Hysteria
battlerites.description: Reduces the cooldown of {2}Panic Flask{-} by {cooldownreduction1}. Direct hits further reduce the cooldown by {cooldownreduction2}.

battlerites.name: Chaos
battlerites.description: {2}Panic Flask{-} explodes upon hitting an enemy, dealing {damage} damage and inflicting {2}Lesser Panic{-} to other nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Deadly Brew
battlerites.description: {2}Panic Flask{-} deals {damage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Swift Roll
battlerites.description: {2}Roll{-} increases movement speed by {hastefactor} for {duration}. Reduces cooldown of {2}Roll{-} by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Sticky Goo
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Snare{-} factor of {2}Crippling Goo{-} from {slowfactor1} to {slowfactor2}.

battlerites.name: Agility
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed by {hastemodifier}.

battlerites.name: Dynamic Solution
battlerites.description: Increases max range and radius of {2}Clarity Potion{-} by {factor}.

ability1.name: Toxic Bolt
ability1.description: Projectile attack that deals {damage} damage and inflicts ^2Toxic^-.

ability2.name: Healing Potion
ability2.description: Throw a potion to target location that heals the nearest ally for {healing} health and applies {2}Revitalize{-}.

ability3.name: Barrier
ability3.description: Grant a {2}Shield{-} to target ally. It absorbs up to {absorb} damage for {duration}.

ability4.name: Clarity Potion
ability4.description: Throw a cleansing potion to target location, knocking nearby enemies away. The impact removes positive effects from enemies and negative effects from allies.

ability5.name: Panic Flask
ability5.description: Throw a chemical flask that deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Panic{-}.

ability6.name: Roll
ability6.description: Roll forward and avoid incoming attacks.

ability7.name: Crippling Goo
ability7.description: Throw a vial of mixed chemicals to target location that deals {impactdamage} damage and inflicts {2}Snare{-} on impact. It covers the ground in a crippling goo that deals {damage} damage and slows enemies over the duration.

characters.name: Sirius
characters.description: Sirius, a calm prodigy who uses the energies of stars and planets as destructive spells and healing powers. The prophecy was true and foretold the birth of the Zenith.

battlerites.name: Debilitating Slash
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Weaken{-} factor by {weakenfactor} and duration by {duration}.

battlerites.name: Radiance
battlerites.description: {2}Sunlight{-} heals you for {bonusheal} health when another ally is healed.

battlerites.name: Sunbath
battlerites.description: Charged {2}Crescent Strike{-} hits empower your next {2}Sunlight{-}, causing {ticks} additional beam to heal the ally nearest the area for {healing1} health.

battlerites.name: Cosmic Reach
battlerites.description: {2}Celestial Split{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and max range increases by {1}20{-}.

battlerites.name: Sunwell
battlerites.description: {2}Celestial Split{-} heals {healing} bonus health. Healing an ally reduces its cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Illumination
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with {2}Sunrise{-} illuminates nearby allies, increasing damage output by {damagefactor} and healing received by {healingfactor} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Sunscreen
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with {2}Sunrise{-} grants nearby allies a {2}Shield{-}. It absorbs up to {damageabsorb} damage for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Daybreak
battlerites.description: {2}Sunrise{-} can be recast for {recastduration} to return to the origin location.

battlerites.name: Lunatic
battlerites.description: {2}Lunar Strike{-} can be recast within {duration} to spawn {2}Lesser Lunar Strike{-} with reduced radius and duration. It does not affect enemies already affected by {2}Lunar Strike{-}.

battlerites.name: Moonlight
battlerites.description: Each enemy hit with {2}Lunar Strike{-} restores {charges} {2}Sunlight{-} charge. Hitting at least one enemy empowers your next {2}Sunlight{-}, causing {ticks} additional beam to heal the ally nearest the area for {healing1} health.

battlerites.name: Moonstone
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Petrify{-} duration by {bonusduration} and reduces cooldown of {2}Lunar Strike{-} by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Celestial Cycle
battlerites.description: {2}Prismatic Strike{-} hits charge your weapon by {chargeup}.

battlerites.name: Gravity
battlerites.description: Each {2}Astral Beam{-} hit inflicts a {slowfactor} {2}Snare{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Saros Slash
battlerites.description: Reduces weapon charge time by {factor} and charged {2}Crescent Strike{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

ability1.name: Crescent Strike
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals {damage} damage. Your weapon charges over time. When fully charged, it deals {bonusdamage} damage and inflicts {2}Weaken{-}.

ability2.name: Sunlight
ability2.description: Call down a beam of sunlight that heals the ally nearest target location for {healing} health.

ability3.name: Celestial Split
ability3.description: Teleport to target location, dealing {damage} damage to nearby enemies and healing nearby allies for {healing} health.

ability4.name: Sunrise
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, teleport to a new location. You heal nearby allies for {healing} health and fully charge your weapon.

ability5.name: Lunar Strike
ability5.description: Call down a ray of moonlight at target location, inflicting {2}Petrify{-} to nearby enemies.

ability6.name: Prismatic Strike
ability6.description: Dash forward and cleave nearby enemies. Deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Fading Snare{-}.

ability7.name: Astral Beam
ability7.description: Channel a beam of light that deals {damage} damage to enemies, heals allies for {healing} health and heals yourself for {selfhealing} health over the duration.

characters.name: Pestilus
characters.description: Pestilus, secret devotee of the evil Rasal, unleashes swarms of insects to infest and cripple his enemies. Advisor to the King of Quna, Pestilus is able to release his innermost darkest desires inside the arena.

battlerites.name: Overlord
battlerites.description: Your movement speed increases by {buffspeedfactor} for each enemy or ally affected by {3}Moth{-}. Stacks up to {maxstacks} times.

battlerites.name: Blood Leecher
battlerites.description: Hitting an ally with {2}Bloodsucker{-} causes you to deal no damage to self.

battlerites.name: Colony
battlerites.description: Hitting a champion affected by {2}Moth{-} or a {2}Queen{-} with {2}Bloodsucker{-} causes {2}Moth{-} to spread to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Insectivore
battlerites.description: Hitting an enemy or ally affected by {2}Moth{-} with {2}Bloodsucker{-} deals {damage} bonus damage to enemies and heals {healing} bonus health to allies.

battlerites.name: Defiler
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Infest{-} duration by {bonusduration}. Drains {healthdrain} health from enemies and heals allies for {healing} health over the duration.

battlerites.name: Spores
battlerites.description: {2}Infest{-} reduces damage and healing output of enemies by {weakenfactor} and increases damage and healing output of allies by {empowerfactor}.

battlerites.name: Scourge
battlerites.description: Allows you to {3}Infest{-} an additional target.

battlerites.name: Hive Mind
battlerites.description: Recasting the {2}Queen{-} commands it to fly towards target location. Reduces cooldown of {2}Queen{-} by {reduction}.

battlerites.name: Swarm Queen
battlerites.description: {2}Queen{-} spawns with a {2}Swarm Shield{-} that absorbs up to {shieldvalue} damage and lasts {duration}.

battlerites.name: Sacrifice
battlerites.description: {2}Queen{-} slows nearby enemies movement speed by {slowfactor} and deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage when it explodes.

battlerites.name: Broodmother
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Queen{-} panic duration by {bonusduration}.

battlerites.name: Spiderling Venom
battlerites.description: {2}Arachnophobia{-} deals {damage} damage. Increases {2}Panic{-} duration by {bonusduration}.

battlerites.name: Egg Carrier
battlerites.description: {2}Arachnophobia{-} bounces forward, causing another impact. The radius of the second impact is {bonusradiusfactor} larger.

battlerites.name: Lord of the Flies
battlerites.description: {2}Scarab{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage or healing and inflicts {2}Fading Blind{-} that reduces enemy sight range by {blindfactor}. Restores sight over {2}Scarab{-} duration.

battlerites.name: Disperse
battlerites.description: Releasing an {2}Infested{-} enemy inflicts a {snarefactor} {2}Snare{-} for {snareduration} and pushes it back in the opposite direction.

ability1.name: Moth
ability1.description: Projectile attack that deals {damage} damage on enemy hit and heals {healing} health on ally hit. Inflicts {2}Moth{-} and heals you for {selfhealing} health.

ability2.name: Bloodsucker
ability2.description: Projectile attack that deals {damage} damage on enemy hit, heals {healing} health on ally hit and deals {selfdamage} damage to self. Cannot deal lethal damage to self.\n\nHitting a {2}Queen{-} with {2}Bloodsucker{-} kills the {2}Queen{-} without dealing any damage to self.

ability3.name: Infest
ability3.description: Lurch forward, inflicting {2}Infest{-} to the first ally or enemy you reach. Heals allies and self for {selfhealing} health on hit. Can be recast to end this effect early.

ability4.name: Queen
ability4.description: Summon a {2}Queen{-} at target location, healing nearby allies for {areahealing} health and {healing} additional health over {duration}.\n\nThe {2}Queen{-} explodes after the duration unless killed by an enemy. The explosion deal {areadamage} damage and inflicts {2}Panic{-} to nearby enemies.

ability5.name: Arachnophobia
ability5.description: Throw a spider egg to target location, inflicting {2}Panic{-} to nearby enemies.

ability6.name: Swarm
ability6.description: Grant a {2}Shield{-} to target ally. It absorbs up to {absorb} damage for {duration} and spreads {3}Moth{-} to nearby enemies if destroyed by damage.

ability7.name: Scarab Pack
ability7.description: Summon and command {amount} {2}Scarabs{-} to attack enemies or aid allies. A {2}Scarab{-} deals {damage} damage on enemy hit and heals {healing} health on ally hit. Scarabs stick to players for a short duration.

characters.name: Blossom
characters.description: Blossom is a happy, bubbly young faun from the Silverdeep Forest. She has left her home to investigate a disturbance in the natural order. She is never far from her bird companion, Maxwell.

battlerites.name: Weakening Pitch
battlerites.description: Charged {2}Thwack!{-} inflicts {2}Weaken{-}, reducing target's damage and healing output by {weakenfactor} for {weakenduration}.

battlerites.name: Nature's Cycle
battlerites.description: Reduces your weapon charge cooldown by {factor}.

battlerites.name: Kindhearted
battlerites.description: {2}Nourish{-} heals {healing} bonus health when healing another ally. {2}Butterflies{-} heals for {healovertime} bonus health.

battlerites.name: Fluttering Grace
battlerites.description: You move {movementspeedfactor} faster for each nearby ally affected by {2}Butterflies{-}.

battlerites.name: Gift of Nature
battlerites.description: {2}Hop{-} causes you to leave behind a {2}Lesser Boom Bloom{-} seed. After {delayduration}, the seed inflicts {2}Stun{-} for {stunduration} on nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Hop and Skip!
battlerites.description: {2}Hop{-} can be recast for a {2}Lesser Hop{-} that travels a shorter distance.

battlerites.name: Nature's Presence
battlerites.description: {2}Hop{-} grants {factor} increased damage and healing output to nearby allies for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Cautious
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Hop{-} invisibility duration by {bonusduration}.

battlerites.name: Healthful Bark
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Tree of Life{-} health by {bonushealth}.

battlerites.name: Refreshing Seed
battlerites.description: {2}Tree of Life{-} grants nearby allies {hastefactor} increased movement speed for {duration} when destroyed or at the end of its duration.

battlerites.name: Bountiful Tree
battlerites.description: Whenever {2}Tree of Life{-} is healed by {2}Nourish{-}, nearby allies are healed for the same amount.

battlerites.name: Spring Growth
battlerites.description: {2}Boom Bloom{-} hits charge your weapon by {weaponchargefactor}.

battlerites.name: Pollen
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Stun{-} duration of {2}Boom Bloom{-} by {duration}.

battlerites.name: Puff
battlerites.description: {2}Gust{-} can be recast to launch a gust of wind. It deals {damage} damage and knocks you and the targets apart.

battlerites.name: Growing Power
battlerites.description: Each consecutive wave of energy from {2}Dance of the Dryads{-} deals {bonusdamage} more damage than the previous.

ability1.name: Thwack!
ability1.description: Throw an infused acorn that deals {damage} damage. Your weapon charges over time. When fully charged, the acorn deals {bonusdamage} damage and inflicts {2}Snare{-}.

tooltipData.Name: Debuff
tooltipData.Value: Reduces target's movement speed by {slowpercent} for {slowduration}.

ability2.name: Nourish
ability2.description: Send natural power to target location, healing the nearest ally for {healing} health. Applies {2}Butterflies{-}.

ability3.name: Hop
ability3.description: Dash towards target location and avoid incoming attacks. Upon landing, become invisible, gain {hastefactor} increased movement speed and remove movement impairing effects. Using any ability ends this effect.

ability4.name: Tree of Life
ability4.description: Summon an immovable {2}Tree of Life{-} sapling that heals nearby allies for {initialhealing} health and {healing} additional health over {duration}.

ability5.name: Boom Bloom
ability5.description: Launch a boom bloom seed, dealing {damage} damage. The seed will take root and bloom after a short delay, inflicting {2}Stun{-} on nearby enemies.

ability6.name: Gust
ability6.description: Summon a barrier of wind that pushes enemies away and reflects projectiles.

ability7.name: Dance of the Dryads
ability7.description: Launch into the air, then unleash a series of {projectileamount} piercing energy waves upon landing. Each wave deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Weaken{-}.

characters.name: Iva
characters.description: A scavenger from the outer realms. Iva has engineered her own arsenal of weapons. Firing crazy rockets or unleashing a storm of bullets is her way of greeting her opponents in the Arena.

battlerites.name: Stockpile
battlerites.description: {2}Rocket X-67{-} gains {amount} ability charge but cooldown increases by {bonuscooldown}.

battlerites.name: Heavy Rocket
battlerites.description: {2}Rocket X-67{-} hits inflict {2}Fading Snare{-} for {gradualslowduration} and the explosion inflicts {2}Fading Snare{-} for {gradualslowduration2}.

battlerites.name: Boom!
battlerites.description: {2}Rocket X-67{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Oil Blaster
battlerites.description: {2}Jet Pack{-} causes your next {2}Boomstick{-} to inflict {2}Oil{-}.

battlerites.name: U-Turn
battlerites.description: Recast {2}Jet Pack{-} to fly back to your starting location.

battlerites.name: Rocket Boosters
battlerites.description: ^2Jet Pack^- increases movement speed by {factor} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Blast Shield
battlerites.description: {2}Zap{-} knocks nearby enemies back and grants {hastefactor} {2}Fading Haste{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Hyperspeed
battlerites.description: {2}Zap{-} increases your {2}Boomstick{-} attack and reload speed by {attackspeedbonus} while you're affected by the {2}Shield{-}.

battlerites.name: Durable Shield
battlerites.description: {2}Zap{-} absorbs {bonusshield} more damage on yourself and {allybonusshield} more damage on other allies.

battlerites.name: Conductor
battlerites.description: {2}Tazer{-} hits bounce once towards a nearby enemy.

battlerites.name: Igniting Spark
battlerites.description: {2}Tazer{-} consumes {2}Oil{-} to inflict {2}Burning Oil{-} and deals {damage} damage on {2}Spell Block{-} interrupts.

battlerites.name: EMP
battlerites.description: {2}Tazer{-} hits remove positive effects from nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Tractor Pulse
battlerites.description: {2}Tractor Beam{-} inflicts {2}Stun{-} for {duration} to enemies caught in the beam when the effect ends and cooldown reduces by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: All Systems Operational
battlerites.description: {2}Machine Gun{-} inflicts {2}Oil{-} to enemies in a frontal cone when activated and launches a {2}Rocket X-67{-} when firing the last bullet.

battlerites.name: Gunge
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Oil{-} factor by {slowfactor} and duration by {bonusduration}.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by {energyfactor} and maximum energy by {energybonus}.

ability1.name: Boomstick
ability1.description: Fire {projectileamount} bullets in a cone, dealing up to {damage} damage.

ability2.name: ROCKET X-67
ability2.description: Launch a rocket that deals {damage} damage. It explodes to deal {aoedamage} damage to other nearby enemies, consuming {2}Oil{-} to inflict {2}Burning Oil{-}.

ability3.name: Jet Pack
ability3.description: Fire up your jet pack and fly to target location. Inflicts {2}Oil{-} on enemies you fly over.

ability4.name: ZAP
ability4.description: Grant a {2}Shield{-} to target ally, removing all negative effects. It absorbs up to {shieldamount} damage and increases movement speed by {hastefactor}.

ability5.name: Tazer
ability5.description: Fire a shot that inflicts {2}Spell Block{-}. When {2}Spell Block{-} interrupts an ability, it inflicts {2}Stun{-}.

ability6.name: Tractor Beam
ability6.description: Channel a beam that drags enemies towards your position while blocking projectile and melee attacks in front of you.

ability7.name: Machine Gun
ability7.description: Fire a series of {bullets} piercing projectiles, dealing a total of {damage} damage.

characters.name: Alysia
characters.description: From the frozen north comes the ice sculptor Alysia. Her power allows her to wield ice with both grace and deadly precision. She can damage and freeze her enemies from a distance, while shielding her allies with ice. Obsessed with shapes and form, she left her icy fortress of solitude to seek inspiration in the arena.

battlerites.name: Crystalline Lattice
battlerites.description: {2}Glacial Prism{-} absorbs up to {bonushealth} more damage and its explosion range is increased by {rangefactor}.

battlerites.name: Ice Breaker
battlerites.description: {2}Ice Lance{-} deals {damage} bonus damage and breaks {2}Freeze{-} before dealing damage.

battlerites.name: Cryogenic Lance
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Chill{-} duration of {2}Ice Lance{-} by {bonuschill}. {2}Ice Lance{-} explodes upon hit or reaching max range to inflict {2}Chill{-} for {duration} on nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Frost Nova
battlerites.description: {2}Arctic Wind{-} inflicts {2}Root{-} for {immobilizeduration}.

battlerites.name: Blizzard
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Flash Freeze{-} radius by {radiusbonus} and reduces cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Figure Skating
battlerites.description: {2}Glacial Prism{-} grants {factor} {2}Fading Haste{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Twirl
battlerites.description: {2}Arctic Wind{-} can be recast to perform a short leap.

battlerites.name: Agility
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed by {hastemodifier}.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by {energyfactor} and maximum energy by {energybonus}.

battlerites.name: Frozen Muse
battlerites.description: Whenever you inflict {2}Freeze{-}, your {2}Frost Bolts{-} are empowered for {duration}. They deal {damage} bonus damage and inflict {2}Chill{-} even on targets without {2}Chill{-}.

battlerites.name: Snowstorm
battlerites.description: {2}Flash Freeze{-} impact leaves a lingering snowstorm that deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Chill{-} over {duration}. The damage affects enemies with {2}Freeze{-} directly.

battlerites.name: Vandalism
battlerites.description: You can break your own ice crown with a single {2}Frost Bolt{-} to launch the cone of icicles.

battlerites.name: Permafrost
battlerites.description: {2}Frozen Gallery{-} inflicts {2}Chill{-} for {duration} to enemies in the area when the path appears. Also increases {2}Freeze{-} duration from {beforeduration} to {afterduration}.

battlerites.name: Wintry Blast
battlerites.description: {2}Glacial Prism{-} deals {damage} damage to nearby enemies when it breaks and {2}Chill{-} duration increases by {chillduration}.

battlerites.name: Arctic Cloak
battlerites.description: Hitting an ally with {2}Flash Freeze{-} applies {2}Lesser Glacial Prism{-}, absorbing up to {shieldamount} damage for {shieldduration}.

battlerites.name: Piercing Cold
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Ice Lance{-} range by {rangefactor}. It pierces enemies and damage reduces {damagereduction} per hit.

ability1.name: Frost Bolt
ability1.description: Launch a cold bolt that deals {damage} damage. Deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and adds {2}Chill{-} duration to enemies affected by {2}Chill{-}.

ability2.name: Ice Lance
ability2.description: Projectile attack that deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Chill{-}. Deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage to enemies already affected by {2}Chill{-}.

ability3.name: Arctic Wind
ability3.description: Inflict {2}Chill{-} to nearby enemies and soar gracefully to target location.

ability4.name: Glacial Prism
ability4.description: Grant a {2}Shield{-} to target ally. It absorbs up to {shieldamount} damage for {duration}. When it breaks, it explodes to inflict {2}Chill{-} on nearby enemies.

ability5.name: Flash Freeze
ability5.description: Call down a frozen star at target location that deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Chill{-} to enemies in the area. Inflicts {2}Freeze{-} to enemies already affected by {2}Chill{-}.

ability6.name: Ice Crown
ability6.description: Launch a fragile sculpture that knocks enemies back and blocks enemy attacks for {duration}. When an enemy breaks it, a cone of icicles shoots forward to deal {damage} damage and inflict {2}Chill{-}.

ability7.name: Frozen Gallery
ability7.description: Mark a path of frost. After a {delay} delay, the path deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Freeze{-} to enemies in the area, turning them into beautiful statues.

characters.name: Rook
characters.description: A mighty chieftain rushing into battle with a giant hammer in one hand and his dinner in the other. Rook likes to smash his enemies, with boulders, with hammers and even with his body. Once he goes berserk he turns into an unstoppable force.

battlerites.name: Pummel Rush
battlerites.description: {2}Pummel{-} hits reduce cooldown of {2}Rush{-} by {duration}.

battlerites.name: Squash
battlerites.description: {2}Crushing Blow{-} inflicts {2}Stun{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Weapon Break
battlerites.description: {2}Crushing Blow{-} deals {damage} bonus damage and enemies affected by {2}Armor Break{-} deal {factor} less damage.

battlerites.name: Rook Smash
battlerites.description: {2}Crushing Blow{-} deals {damage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Endurance
battlerites.description: {2}Rush{-} cooldown reduces by {cooldownreduction}. Using {2}Rush{-} without hitting an enemy further reduces cooldown by {maxcooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Raging Bull
battlerites.description: During {2}Berserk{-}, {2}Rush{-} cast time and cooldown reduces by {reductionfactor}.

battlerites.name: Frenzy
battlerites.description: {2}Rush{-} hits cause you to gain {2}Berserk{-} for {berserkduration}.

battlerites.name: Madness
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed bonus during {2}Berserk{-} by {hastefactor}.

battlerites.name: Giant
battlerites.description: Decreases damage taken during {2}Berserk{-} by {factor}.

battlerites.name: War Cry
battlerites.description: {2}Berserk{-} inflicts {slowpercent} {2}Snare{-} for {slowduration} to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Crag
battlerites.description: {2}Boulder Toss{-} inflicts {2}Fading Snare{-} for {duration}. Also reduces its cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Crumble
battlerites.description: {2}Boulder Toss{-} deals {damage} bonus damage and inflicts {2}Armor Break{-}.

battlerites.name: Earthquake
battlerites.description: {2}Tremor{-} inflicts {2}Armor Break{-}.

ability1.name: Pummel
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals {damage1} damage. Successful hits reduce cooldown of {2}Crushing Blow{-} by {cooldownreduction}.

ability2.name: Crushing Blow
ability2.description: Jump into the air, then slam your mace into the ground. Deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Armor Break{-} to enemies in the area.

ability3.name: Rush
ability3.description: Rush forward and slam into an enemy. Deals {mindamage}-{maxdamage} damage and inflicts {2}Stun{-}. Damage increases with travel distance.

ability4.name: Berserk
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, become invulnerable for {invulnerableduration} and gain {2}Berserk{-}.

ability5.name: Boulder Toss
ability5.description: Toss a boulder to target location that deals {damage} to nearby enemies and knocks them back.

ability6.name: Smack
ability6.description: Smack enemies with your meat to deal {damage} damage and knock them back. Knocking an enemy into a wall inflicts {2}Incapacitate{-}.

ability7.name: Tremor
ability7.description: Jump into the air and slam your hammer into the ground {times} times. The shockwave deals {damage1} / {damage2} / {damage3} damage.

characters.name: Jade
characters.description: A mysterious gunslinger. Born with eagle-eyes and armed with a lethal sniper rifle, Jade's pinpoint accuracy is a serious threat for anyone who enters the arena. For close encounters, she prefers a combination of stealth and trusty homemade revolvers.

battlerites.name: Gunslinger
battlerites.description: {2}Revolver Shot{-} hits reduce cooldown of {2}Stealth{-} by {cooldownreduction}. Cooldown can't be reduced during {2}Stealth{-}.

battlerites.name: Deadly Focus
battlerites.description: ^2Snipe^- deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Shadow Shot
battlerites.description: {2}Snipe{-} hits heal you for {healing} health.

battlerites.name: Surprise Shot
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Stun{-} duration of {2}Snipe{-} by {bonusduration1}, and further increases it by {bonusduration2} when fired from {2}Stealth{-}.

battlerites.name: Concussion Bomb
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Stun{-} duration of {2}Blast Vault{-} by {duration}.

battlerites.name: Explosive Jump
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Blast Vault{-} max range by {1}20{-} and reduces cooldown by {reduction}.

battlerites.name: Blasting Pistols
battlerites.description: {2}Blast Vault{-} causes your next {shots} {2}Revolver Shots{-} to deal {bonusdamage} bonus damage and grant {bonusenergy} bonus energy.

battlerites.name: Ambush
battlerites.description: {2}Stealth{-} reduces the cooldown of {2}Snipe{-} by {reduction}. Also increases duration of invisibility by {duration}.\n

battlerites.name: Farewell Present
battlerites.description: {2}Stealth{-} causes you to drop a bomb that explodes after {impactdelay}, dealing {damage} damage and inflicting {2}Fading Snare{-} for {slowduration} to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Through the Shadows
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Fading Haste{-} factor of {2}Stealth{-} by {haste2}.

battlerites.name: Desperado
battlerites.description: {2}Disabling Shot{-} hits instantly reload {2}Revolver Shot{-} with {charges} ammo.

battlerites.name: Delight
battlerites.description: {2}Disabling Shot{-} hits heal you for {impacthealing} health and {2}Spell Block{-} interrupts heal you for {interrupthealing} bonus health.

battlerites.name: Magic Bullet
battlerites.description: {2}Disabling Shot{-} pierces enemies. Also increases its range by {bonusrange}.

battlerites.name: Black Powder
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Junk Shot{-} knockback force by {knockbackbonus}. Knocking an enemy into a wall inflicts {2}Stun{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Shrapnel
battlerites.description: {2}Explosive Shells{-} inflicts {slowpercent} {2}Snare{-} for {slowduration}.

battlerites.name: Agility
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed by {hastemodifier}.

ability1.name: Revolver Shot
ability1.description: Fire a revolver shot dealing {damage} damage.

ability2.name: Snipe
ability2.description: Fire a piercing bullet that deals {damage} damage and inflicts ^2Stun^-.

ability3.name: Blast Vault
ability3.description: Detonate a grenade that launches you into the air. The explosion deals {damage} damage and inflicts ^2Stun^- on nearby enemies.

ability4.name: Stealth
ability4.description: Become invisible, gain {2}Fading Haste{-}, and remove movement impairing effects.

ability5.name: Disabling Shot
ability5.description: Fire a shot that inflicts {2}Snare{-} and {2}Spell Block{-}. When {2}Spell Block{-} interrupts an ability, it inflicts {2}Silence{-}.

ability6.name: Junk Shot
ability6.description: Fire {bulletcount} piercing bullets in a cone, dealing up to {damage} damage and knocking enemies back.

ability7.name: Explosive Shells
ability7.description: Fire a series of {shells} explosive shells, dealing a total of {damage} damage and {aoedamage} damage to nearby enemies.

characters.name: Ruh Kaan
characters.description: Ruh Kaan was awoken when a grave robber desecrated the sacred crypts Ark’dun. Pursuing the trespasser led him to the Arenas where he is still tracking his quarry. He wields his dark powers to remove those who would stand in his way, taking great pleasure in consuming their souls.

battlerites.name: Wicked Strike
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Silence{-} duration from {oldduration} to {newduration}.

battlerites.name: Leech Blade
battlerites.description: Hitting {2}Cursed{-} enemies with {2}Defiled Blade{-} heals for {bonushealingperhit} bonus health. Charged {2}Defiled Blade{-} hits also heal for {bonushealing} bonus health.

battlerites.name: Grim Edge
battlerites.description: Charged {2}Defiled Blade{-} deals {damage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Agony
battlerites.description: {2}Shadow Bolts{-} deal {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Affliction
battlerites.description: {2}Shadow Bolt{-} inflicts {2}Amplify{-}, increasing all damage the target receives by {factor} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Nether Chains
battlerites.description: {2}Sinister Strike{-} inflicts {2}Curse{-}.

battlerites.name: Demonic Hunt
battlerites.description: {2}Sinister Strike{-} gains {charges} ability charge, but increases its cooldown by {cooldownincrease}.

battlerites.name: Shadow Fury
battlerites.description: Negating an attack with {2}Consume{-} grants {charges} ability charges for {2}Shadowbolt{-}.

battlerites.name: Gorge
battlerites.description: Reduces cooldown of {2}Consume{-} by {staticcooldownreduction}. Negating attacks further reduces the cooldown by {cooldownreduction}{2}s{-}.

battlerites.name: Death Grip
battlerites.description: {2}Claw of the Wicked{-} cooldown is reduced by {cooldownreduction1} and hitting a target further reduces its cooldown by {cooldownreduction2}.

battlerites.name: Cold Embrace
battlerites.description: {2}Claw of the Wicked{-} inflicts both {2}Root{-} for {immobilizeduration} and {2}Curse{-}.

battlerites.name: Tenacious Demon
battlerites.description: {2}Claw of the Wicked{-} deals {drain} bonus damage. Increases range by {rangefactor}.

battlerites.name: Hunger
battlerites.description: Activating {2}Shadow Beast{-} pulls nearby enemies towards you.

battlerites.name: Shadow Prowl
battlerites.description: {2}Shadow Beast{-} increases movement speed by {hastefactor}.

battlerites.name: Reaper
battlerites.description: Reduces your weapon charge cooldown by {factor}.

battlerites.name: Night Stalker
battlerites.description: Your movement speed increases by {basefactor} and is increased {factor} further while your weapon is fully charged.

ability1.name: Defiled Blade
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals {damage} damage. Your weapon charges over time. When fully charged, it deals {bonusdamage} damage, inflicts both {2}Curse{-} and {2}Silence{-}, and heals you for {healing} health on hit.

ability2.name: Shadowbolt
ability2.description: Launch a dark bolt of energy that deals {damage} damage.

ability3.name: Sinister Strike
ability3.description: Dash forward, then deal {damage} damage to nearby enemies.

ability4.name: Consume
ability4.description: Negate melee and projectile attacks in front of you, inflicting {2}Fading Snare{-} on enemy melee attackers. Negating an attack fully charges your weapon and resets the cooldown of {2}Shadowbolt{-}.

ability5.name: Claw of the Wicked
ability5.description: Launch a claw that deals {damage} damage and pulls an enemy towards you. Heals self equal to damage dealt.

ability6.name: Nether Void
ability6.description: Warp to target location and unleash a shadow blast that inflicts {2}Curse{-} on nearby enemies.

ability7.name: Shadow Beast
ability7.description: Transform into a shadow beast. Replaces {2}Defiled Blade{-} with a cleave attack and {2}Shadowbolt{-} with a pulling projectile attack. All your other abilities are disabled when transformed except {2}Sinister Strike{-}. Recast to end this effect early.

characters.name: Oldur
characters.description: Oldur, a mysterious creature able to bend time and space. He can mend wounds with powerful heals and reverse enemy attacks by freezing them in time.

battlerites.name: Shared Fate
battlerites.description: {2}Time Bomb{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and also deals its damage to nearby enemies when it detonates.

battlerites.name: Dehydration
battlerites.description: {2}Time Bomb{-} reduces incoming healing by {healingmodifier} and outgoing damage by {damagemodifier}.

battlerites.name: Rewind
battlerites.description: {2}Rejuvenating Sand{-} reduces ally's ability cooldowns by {factor}.

battlerites.name: Renew
battlerites.description: {2}Rejuvenate{-} heals for an additional {healfactor} of damage taken over its duration. Restores up to a maximum of {maxhealing} bonus health.

battlerites.name: Recreate
battlerites.description: Passing through an ally with {2}Shifting Sands{-} grants you and your ally a {2}Shield{-} that absorbs up to {health} damage for {duration}.\n

battlerites.name: Chrono Shift
battlerites.description: ^2Shifting Sands^- creates a ^2Lesser Chronoflux^- that reflects projectiles and slows movement speed.

battlerites.name: Sandstorm
battlerites.description: {2}Shifting Sands{-} causes your next {2}Sands of Time{-} to deal {bonusdamage} bonus damage and inflict {2}Fading Snare{-} for {snareduration}.

battlerites.name: Time Walker
battlerites.description: Negating an attack with {2}Time Bender{-} reduces cooldown of {2}Shifting Sands{-} by {reduction}.

battlerites.name: Drain
battlerites.description: Negating attacks with {2}Time Bender{-} grants you a {2}Shield{-} that absorbs up to {shieldamounts} damage for {duration}. Shield value is reduced for each negated attack.

battlerites.name: Stolen Power
battlerites.description: When you capture a projectile with {2}Time Bender{-}, your damage and healing output are increased by {powerfactor} while the projectile is stored in your hourglass.

battlerites.name: Sand Tomb
battlerites.description: {2}Quicksand{-} inflicts {2}Root{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Sand Struck
battlerites.description: {2}Quicksand{-} can be recast to throw {2}Lesser Quicksand{-}. It applies {2}Time Bomb{-} instead of consuming it.

battlerites.name: Time Burst
battlerites.description: Consuming {2}Time Bomb{-} with {2}Quicksand{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Reversal
battlerites.description: {2}Time Travel{-} heals ally for {factor} of all health lost during the previous {duration}.

battlerites.name: Eternal Dunes
battlerites.description: Each enemy hit by {2}Quicksand{-} grants {chargeamount} {2}Rejuvenating Sands{-} charge.

ability1.name: Sands of Time
ability1.description: Launch a projectile that deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Time Bomb{-}.

ability2.name: Rejuvenating Sand
ability2.description: Throw rejuvenating sand to target location that heals the nearest ally for {healing} health and applies {2}Rejuvenate{-}.

ability3.name: Shifting Sands
ability3.description: Turn into sand and travel to target location. Heals allies you pass through for {healing} health and deals {damage} to enemies you pass through.

ability4.name: Time Bender
ability4.description: Negate projectile and melee attacks in front of you. Knock enemy melee attackers back and capture the first negated projectile within your hourglass. Recast this to launch the captured projectile.

ability5.name: Quicksand
ability5.description: Throw an hourglass to target location, exploding to deal {damage} damage and inflict {2}Fading Snare{-}. Consumes {2}Time Bomb{-} to deal its damage instantly.

ability6.name: Stone Glass
ability6.description: Melee area attack that inflicts {2}Stone Glass{-} and knocks enemies back.

ability7.name: Time Travel
ability7.description: Target ally's cooldowns are reduced by {cooldownacceleration}. That ally is removed from the fight for a short duration before reappearing at target location of their choice, inflicting {2}Stun{-} to nearby enemies.

characters.name: Ashka
characters.description: A masked creature specialized in dark sorcery and pyro-kinetic powers. Casts devastating fire spells on his opponents and avoids close combat. Don't be fooled by his size, Ashka's inner demon strikes fear into all who face him.

battlerites.name: Combustion
battlerites.description: {2}Fire Storm{-} hits deal {searingheatbonusdamage} bonus damage and spread fire to other nearby enemies, dealing {areadamage} damage and inflicting {2}Ignite{-}.

battlerites.name: Wildfire
battlerites.description: {2}Fire Storm{-} launches {1}1{-} additional projectile but increases its cooldown by {cooldownincrease}.

battlerites.name: Heat
battlerites.description: {2}Fire Storm{-} can be cast while moving at {fastspeedfactor} movement speed and {speedfactor} while channeling.

battlerites.name: Burning Feet
battlerites.description: {2}Searing Flight{-} increases movement speed by {speedmodifier} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Blaze
battlerites.description: {2}Searing Flight{-} causes your next {2}Fireball{-} to deal {bonusdamage} bonus damage and inflict {2}Ignite{-}.

battlerites.name: Fire Ward
battlerites.description: {2}Searing Flight{-} grants a {2}Shield{-}. It absorbs up to {damageabsorb} damage for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Eruption
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Flamestrike{-} radius by {radiusbonus} and reduces cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Inferno
battlerites.description: {2}Flamestrike{-} deals {damage} bonus damage and inflicts {2}Ignite{-}.

battlerites.name: Ember Fire
battlerites.description: {2}Flamestrike{-} heals you for {healfactor} of damage dealt.

battlerites.name: Lava Punch
battlerites.description: Reduces cooldown of {2}Molten Fist{-} by {basecooldownreduction}. Hitting an enemy further reduces cooldown by {cooldownreductiononhit}.

battlerites.name: Knockout
battlerites.description: Knocking an enemy into a wall using {2}Molten Fist{-} inflicts {2}Stun{-} for {stunduration}.

battlerites.name: Fire Punch
battlerites.description: {2}Molten Fist{-} travel distance increases by {distancefactor} and knockback force increases by {knockbackfactor}.

battlerites.name: Conflagration
battlerites.description: {2}Fireballs{-} traveling through {2}Firewall{-} turn into {2}Fire Storm{-} bolts.

battlerites.name: Raging Fire
battlerites.description: {2}Infernal Scorch{-} causes your {2}Fireballs{-} to turn into {2}Fire Storm{-} bolts for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Magma
battlerites.description: {2}Ignite{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage when first applied and reduces target's movement speed by {slowfactor}.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by {energyfactor} and maximum energy by {energybonus}.

ability1.name: Fireball
ability1.description: Launch a fireball that deals {damage} damage and reapplies {2}Ignite{-}.

ability2.name: Fire Storm
ability2.description: Fire a series of {ticks} flame bolts. Each bolt deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Ignite{-}.

ability3.name: Searing Flight
ability3.description: Transform into fire and travel to target location, dealing {damage} damage to nearby enemies.

ability4.name: Flamestrike
ability4.description: Engulf target location in flames, dealing {aoedamage} damage and inflicting {2}Stun{-} to enemies in the area.

ability5.name: Molten Fist
ability5.description: Turn into a fist of magma and dash forward. Inflicts {2}Snare{-} and knocks the enemy back.

ability6.name: Firewall
ability6.description: Summon a firewall at target location. It blocks projectiles and inflicts {2}Ignite{-} to enemies that enter.

ability7.name: Infernal Scorch
ability7.description: Turn into a fire elemental and dash forward to deal {damage} damage and inflict {2}Stun{-}. Leave a trail of scorched earth, dealing {totaldamage} damage and inflicting {2}Ignite{-} to enemies in the area over {totalduration}.

characters.name: Varesh
characters.description: A being formed by the energies of others. Varesh uses his power  to weaken and disrupt his enemies. By combining his powers he is able to unleash devastating attacks.

battlerites.name: Unlimited Power
battlerites.description: Consuming {2}Corruption{-} with {2}Shatter{-} increases {2}Fading Snare{-} duration from {snareduration1} to {snareduration2} and reapplies {2}Corruption{-}.

battlerites.name: Fervor
battlerites.description: Consuming {2}Corruption{-} increases your movement speed by {hastefactor} for {duration}. Can stack up to {maxstacks} times.

battlerites.name: Silence
battlerites.description: Consuming {2}Judgement{-} with {2}Shatter{-} increases {2}Silence{-} duration from {silenceduration1} to {silenceduration2}.

battlerites.name: Devastation
battlerites.description: {2}Hand of Judgement{-} deals {damage} bonus damage and hitting an enemy resets its cooldown.

battlerites.name: Return
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with {2}Wuju{-} allows you to recast it for {recastduration}.

battlerites.name: Ruin
battlerites.description: ^2Wuju^- inflicts ^2Judgement^- on enemies struck.

battlerites.name: Zeal
battlerites.description: Applying {2}Inhibitor's Guard{-} consumes {2}Corruption{-} on nearby enemies, inflicting {2}Fading Snare{-} for {duration}. Heal the shielded ally for {healing} health for each {2}Corruption{-} consumed.

battlerites.name: Celerity
battlerites.description: {2}Inhibitor's Guard{-} increases movement speed by {hastefactor} and damage output by {damagefactor}.

battlerites.name: Wonder
battlerites.description: {2}Inhibitor's Guard{-} absorbs {health} more damage.

battlerites.name: Law Bender
battlerites.description: Each {2}Corruption{-} or {2}Judgement{-} consumed by {2}Shatter{-} reduces {2}Inhibitors Guard{-} cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Fracture
battlerites.description: Ability charges of {2}Shatter{-} increase to {abilitycharges2} from {abilitycharges1}, and {2}Shatter{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Inhibitor
battlerites.description: {2}Shatter{-} can be cast while moving at {speedfactor} speed.

battlerites.name: Kinetic Corruption
battlerites.description: Reduces cooldown of {2}Kinetic Energy{-} by {cooldownreduction}. Inflicts {2}Corruption{-} on enemies hit.

battlerites.name: Absolute Power
battlerites.description: {2}Powers Combined{-} repeats itself {extrarepetition} extra time.

battlerites.name: Synergy
battlerites.description: While both {2}Corruption{-} and {2}Judgement{-} are active on an enemy, their factors are increased by {factorbonus} and both effects are reapplied by {2}Hand of Corruption / Judgement{-} when hitting that enemy.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by {energyfactor} and maximum energy by {energybonus}.

ability1.name: Hand of Corruption
ability1.description: Fire a projectile that deals {damage} damage, inflicts {2}Corruption{-} and heals self for {heal} health on hit.

ability2.name: Hand of Judgement
ability2.description: Fire a projectile that deals {damage} damage and inflicts ^2Judgement^-.

ability3.name: Inhibitor's Guard
ability3.description: Grant a {2}Shield{-} to target ally. It absorbs up to {shieldamount} damage for {duration}.

ability4.name: Wuju
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, teleport to target location and knocks nearby enemies away.\n\nConsumes {2}Corruption{-} to heal you for {healing} health and inflict {2}Fading Snare{-}. Consumes {2}Judgement{-} to deal {bonusdamage} bonus damage and inflict {2}Silence{-}.

ability5.name: Shatter
ability5.description: Spawn an exploding shard at target location, dealing {aoedamage} damage to enemies in the area.\n\nConsumes {2}Corruption{-} to heal you for {healing} health and inflict {2}Fading Snare{-}. Consumes {2}Judgement{-} to deal {bonusdamage} bonus damage and inflict {2}Silence{-}.

ability6.name: Kinetic Energy
ability6.description: Turn immaterial and dash towards target location. Spawns a {2}Shatter{-} shard under each enemy you pass through.

ability7.name: Powers Combined
ability7.description: Turn immaterial and dash forward in target direction, dealing {damage} damage and inflicting both {2}Judgement{-} and {2}Corruption{-}. This effect repeats itself up to {1}3{-} times as long as an enemy is hit.

characters.name: Pearl
characters.description: A sage able to control the oceans and whatever creatures that lurk below. Pearl transforms water into volatile attacks, rejuvenating streams and protecting bubbles.

battlerites.name: Soaking Wet
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Silence{-} duration from {silencedurationoriginal} to {silenceduration}.

battlerites.name: Rippling Waters
battlerites.description: Firing {2}Volatile Water{-} through a {2}Bubble Barrier{-} increases damage by {bonusdamage} and range by {bonusrange}.

battlerites.name: Splash Damage
battlerites.description: Charged {2}Volatile Water{-} explodes upon hitting an enemy, dealing full damage and inflicting {2}Silence{-} to other nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Fountain
battlerites.description: {2}Healing Wave{-} bounces to a nearby ally after healing, healing them for {fountainheal} health.

battlerites.name: Spring Water
battlerites.description: {2}Dive{-} heals self for {selfhealing} health and other nearby allies for {areahealing} health when emerging from the deep.

battlerites.name: Ocean Tide
battlerites.description: Diving into a {2}Bubble Barrier{-} destroys the bubble and resets the cooldown of {2}Dive{-}.

battlerites.name: Riptide
battlerites.description: {2}Dive{-} deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Root{-} for {duration} at your starting location.

battlerites.name: Sea Bubble
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with {2}Tidal Wave{-} spawns a {2}Lesser Bubble Barrier{-} around you.

battlerites.name: Gush
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with {2}Tidal Wave{-} recharges your staff.

battlerites.name: Tsunami
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with {2}Tidal Wave{-} fires a volley of {2}Lesser Volatile Water{-} at nearby enemies. Each {2}Lesser Volatile Water{-} deals {damage} damage.

battlerites.name: Ocean Sage
battlerites.description: {2}Bubble Barrier{-} can be recast within {recastduration} to spawn a {2}Lesser Bubble Barrier{-}.

battlerites.name: Tasty Fish
battlerites.description: {2}Bubble Barrier{-} spawns a tasty fish that heals {healing} health and increases damage output by {damagefactor} for {buffduration} when picked up.

battlerites.name: Water Walk
battlerites.description: Touching a {2}Bubble Barrier{-} grants allies a {factor} {2}Haste{-} that fades over {duration} after leaving the bubble.

battlerites.name: Terror from the Deep
battlerites.description: {2}Jaws{-} maximum spew range increases by {bonusrange} and inflicts {slowfactor} {2}Snare{-} for {duration} after enemies land.

ability1.name: Volatile Water
ability1.description: Launch a projectile that deals {damage} damage. Deals {chargeddamage} damage and inflicts {2}Silence{-} if your staff is charged.

ability2.name: Healing Wave
ability2.description: Channel a healing wave to target location that heals the nearest ally for {healing} health over {channelduration}.

ability3.name: Dive
ability3.description: Dive into a pool of water and travel to target location. Recharges your staff.

ability4.name: Tidal Wave
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, heal yourself for {healing} health and send out a tidal wave. It deals {damage} damage to nearby enemies and knocks them back.

ability5.name: Bubble Barrier
ability5.description: Spawn a bubble barrier at target location that knocks players back. The bubble slows enemy projectiles and enemies inside it.

ability6.name: Bubble Shield
ability6.description: Grant a {2}Shield{-} to target ally, removing all negative effects. It absorbs up to {shieldamount} damage for {duration}.

ability7.name: Jaws
ability7.description: Summon Jaws from the depths to devour enemies at target location, dealing {impactdamage} damage. Devoured enemies are removed from battle until Jaws spews them out, dealing {damage} damage to enemies near the landing site. Can be recast to choose a landing site.

characters.name: Destiny
characters.description: An elite sky ranger from the secluded, invisible city of Enza. Many years of rigorous combat training using Magi-tech weaponry makes Destiny an agile and deadly force to be reckoned with. Fed up with the strict regulations of living in Enza, Destiny often escapes the city to blow off some steam and have fun in the arena.

battlerites.name: Plasma Infusion
battlerites.description: Firing {2}Power Blaster{-} through a {2}Plasma Wall{-} increases the range by {bonusrange} and grants you a shield absorbing {shieldvalue} damage on hit.

battlerites.name: Power Attachment
battlerites.description: {2}Charged Bolt{-} deals {mindamage} - {maxdamage} bonus damage, based on charge-up duration.

battlerites.name: System Shock
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Silence{-} duration caused by {2}Spell Block{-} from {silenceduration1} to {silenceduration2}.

battlerites.name: Sizzle
battlerites.description: {2}Plasma Wall{-} deals {damage} damage to enemies that pass through. Increases {2}Snare{-} factor from {slowfactor1} to {slowfactor2} and duration from {duration1} to {duration2}.

battlerites.name: Violent Revolution
battlerites.description: Increases knockback force of {2}Magnetic Orb{-} by {knockbackbonus} and it deals {damage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Globetrotter
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Magnetic Orb{-} duration by {duration} and its movement speed bonus by {bonushastefactor}.

battlerites.name: Dispatch
battlerites.description: {2}Magnetic Orb{-} can be recast to leap to target location, knocking nearby enemies back upon landing.

battlerites.name: Plasma Booster
battlerites.description: Allies that move through {2}Plasma Wall{-} have movement speed increased by {hastefactor} and are granted a {2}Shield{-} for {duration}. The {2}Shield{-} absorbs up to {shieldamount} damage.

battlerites.name: Expansion Pack
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Fading Snare{-} duration of {2}Mega Sphere{-} by {bonusduration} and reduces its cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Energy Conversion
battlerites.description: {2}Sky Strike{-} grants you a shield that absorbs up to {startvalue} damage and absorbs an additional {shieldvalue} damage for each enemy hit. Lasts for {shieldduration}.

battlerites.name: Blast Processing
battlerites.description: {2}Sky Strike{-} deals {damage} bonus damage. Also increases its radius by {radiusincrease}.

battlerites.name: Lasting Plasma
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Plasma Wall{-} duration by {duration} and reduces its cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Transformer
battlerites.description: Maximum amount of {2}Pinball{-} bounces increases by {bonusbounces} and transforms you into {2}Magnetic Orb{-} at the end of duration.

ability1.name: Power Blaster
ability1.description: Projectile attack that deals {damage} damage. Successful hits reduce cooldown of {2}Charged Bolt{-} by {cooldownreduction}.

ability2.name: Charged Bolt
ability2.description: Hold to charge a projectile for up to {maxchargeduration} to increase damage and range. It deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Spell Block{-}. When {2}Spell Block{-} interrupts an ability, it inflicts {2}Silence{-}.\n

ability3.name: Magnetic Orb
ability3.description: Compress yourself into an orb. Removes movement impairing effects and increases movement speed by {hastefactor}. Deals {damage} damage to the first enemy hit and knocks them back.

ability4.name: Sky Strike
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, vault into the air. Then, jump towards move direction and fire a plasma blast at target location that deals {damage} damage and knocks enemies back.

ability5.name: Plasma Wall
ability5.description: Deploy a {2}Plasma Wall{-} at target location. The wall reduces enemy projectile speed and inflicts {2}Snare{-} to enemies that pass through it.

ability6.name: Mega Sphere
ability6.description: Fire a huge energy sphere towards target location. Hitting the {2}Mega Sphere{-} with {2}Power Blaster{-} or {2}Charged Bolt{-} causes an explosion, dealing the fired projectile's effects to all nearby enemies along with {damage} bonus damage and inflicting {2}Fading Snare{-}.

ability7.name: Pinball
ability7.description: Compress yourself into an orb and dash forward at supersonic speed. Deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Stun{-}. Damage is reduced for each target and wall hit, but is not reduced below {mindamage}. Bounces off walls up to a total of {bounces} times.

characters.name: Zander
characters.description: When the famous theatre troupe "The Phantomime Masquerade" disbanded after a series of tragic events, their magnificent magician Zander vanished without a trace. Known for his unparalleled perfection in card trickery, teleportation, duplication and transformation, this distinguished illusionist has now returned from the dead to turn the otherwise ceremonial arenas world-wide into spectacular revelries.

battlerites.name: Phantasmagoria
battlerites.description: Increase the health of {2}Mirror Image{-} illusions by {health} and duration by {duration}.

battlerites.name: Showdown
battlerites.description: Grants self or allies traveling through your {2}Portal{-} a shield that absorbs up to {shieldvalue} damage for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Lasting Form
battlerites.description: Duration of {2}Sheep Trick{-} is increased by {bonusduration} and is further extended by {bonusduration2} if the target is inflicted with {2}Arcane Catalyst{-}.

battlerites.name: Bunny Hop
battlerites.description: Recast {2}Rabbit Form{-} to dash forward, knocking back yourself and target enemy upon hit, interrupting any ability being cast. Inflicts a {stunduration} {2}Stun{-} if enemy is knocked into a wall.

battlerites.name: Ace up the Sleeve
battlerites.description: Traveling through a portal resets the cooldown of {2}Grand Conjuration{-}.

battlerites.name: Arcane Conductor
battlerites.description: Increases the duration of {2}Arcane Catalyst{-} by {bonusduration} and damage taken by {bonusfactor}.

battlerites.name: Poof!
battlerites.description: Your {2}Illusions{-} explode at the end of their duration, dealing {damage} damage and inflicting a {stunduration} {2}Stun{-} to nearby enemies. {2}Grand Illusion{-} explosions are bigger, deal {bigdamage} damage and inflict a {bigstunduration} {2}Stun{-}.

battlerites.name: Lead Astray
battlerites.description: {2}Sheep Trick{-} inflicts {2}Arcane Catalyst{-} on targets hit.

battlerites.name: Late to the Show
battlerites.description: Teleporting yourself or an ally with {2}Portal{-} grants target a {hastefactor} {2}Fading Haste{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Transformation Sickness
battlerites.description: Decreases enemy movement speed by {slowfactor} during {2}Sheep Trick{-}.

battlerites.name: Heart Restoration
battlerites.description: {2}Hearts{-} restores {hothealing} health over the duration.

battlerites.name: Stacked Deck
battlerites.description: Your first {2}Trick Shot{-} after using {2}Mirror Image{-} includes an additional card for both you and your illusion.

battlerites.name: Three of a Kind
battlerites.description: {2}Grand Illusion{-} receives a {duration} shield when conjured, absorbing up to {shieldvalue} damage and throws one extra card when copying {2}Trick Shot{-}.

battlerites.name: Around the World
battlerites.description: Increases cast range and teleport range of {2}Portal{-} by {rangebonus}.

battlerites.name: Arcane Shenanigans
battlerites.description: Allows {2}Grand Conjuration{-} to bounce once upon wall hit and increases its max range by {rangefactor}. Can still only hit once per enemy.

ability1.name: Trick Shot
ability1.description: Throw two magical cards. Each card deals {damage} damage to enemies, heals {healing} health on allies, and heals you for {selfhealing} health on hit. Applies {2}Hearts{-} upon allies hit.

ability2.name: Grand Conjuration
ability2.description: A heavy magical projectile that deals {damage} damage and pierces enemies. Inflicts {2}Arcane Catalyst{-} on targets hit.

ability3.name: Mirror Image
ability3.description: Turn immaterial and dash in target direction, leaving an {2}Illusion{-} where you stood.

ability4.name: Portal
ability4.description: Place a portal at target location that teleports allies one at a time, removing them from the fight for {portaldelay} before reappearing at a target destination of their choice. Teleporting an {2}Illusion{-} increases its duration by {durationincrease} and grants you the ability to recast {2}Portal{-} to pick its target destination.\n

ability5.name: Sheep Trick
ability5.description: Turn enemies inside target area into harmless creatures, rendering them unable to use any abilities for {duration}. If the target takes {damagelimit} damage, the effect is broken.

ability6.name: Rabbit Form
ability6.description: Turn into a rabbit to increase movement speed by {hastefactor}, apply {2}Hearts{-} and remove any movement impairing effects. Knocks away nearby enemies.

ability7.name: The Prestige
ability7.description: Conjure a {2}Grand Illusion{-} at target position.

characters.name: Taya
characters.description: An exceptionally swift hunter wielding a razor sharp boomerang. By shaping the wind around her Taya is able to increase her speed and control her boomerang with deadly precision.

battlerites.name: Breath of Air
battlerites.description: During {2}Haste{-}, the first hit of each {2}Razor Boomerang{-} heals you for {healing} health.

battlerites.name: Cold Wind
battlerites.description: During {2}Haste{-}, {2}Razor Boomerang{-} inflicts {2}Fading Snare{-} for {gradualslowduration}.

battlerites.name: Cross Cut
battlerites.description: {2}X-Strike{-} boomerangs each deal {damage} bonus damage, and an additional {bonusdamage} bonus damage if both boomerangs hit at the intersection.

battlerites.name: Surprise Attack
battlerites.description: During {2}Haste{-}, {2}X-Strike{-} can be used while moving at {speedfactor} movement speed.

battlerites.name: Heavy Boomerangs
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Stun{-} duration of {2}X-Strike{-} by {bonusduration}, and an additional {intersectbonusduration} if both boomerangs hit at the intersection.

battlerites.name: Tailwind
battlerites.description: ^2Haste^- increases the movement speed of nearby allies by {factor} for {duration}.\n

battlerites.name: Gale
battlerites.description: {2}Haste{-} spawns a gale that slows enemy projectiles for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Wind Fury
battlerites.description: During {2}Haste{-}, {2}Wind Strike{-} hits reapply {2}Haste{-}.

battlerites.name: Cyclone
battlerites.description: {2}Wind Strike{-} inflicts {2}Stun{-} for {stunduration} to enemies knocked into walls.

battlerites.name: Vortex
battlerites.description: ^2Wind Bomb^- spawns a vortex that pulls enemies towards its center for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Tracking
battlerites.description: {2}Razor Boomerang{-} hits while mounted deal {bonusdamage} bonus damage and extend the shield duration by {duration}, up to {maxhits} times.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by {energyfactor} and maximum energy by {energybonus}.

battlerites.name: Wind Stream
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Wind Stream{-} duration by {bonusduration} and the {2}Haste{-} duration it grants by {bonushasteduration}.

battlerites.name: Throwing Technique
battlerites.description: Increases maximum range of {2}X-Strike{-} by {bonusrange}.

battlerites.name: Turbulence
battlerites.description: Hitting an enemy with {2}Wind Strike{-} causes your next {2}Razor Boomerang{-} to deal {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

ability1.name: Razor Boomerang
ability1.description: Throw a piercing boomerang that deals {damage} damage and returns upon reaching maximum distance.

ability2.name: X-Strike
ability2.description: Throw two boomerangs in an arc. Each boomerang deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Stun{-} on the way out. Deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage if both boomerangs hit at the intersection.

ability3.name: Haste
ability3.description: Gain {2}Haste{-} and remove movement impairing effects. During {2}Haste{-}, {2}Razor Boomerang{-} deals bonus damage and can be used while moving.

ability4.name: Wind Strike
ability4.description: Spinning melee attack that deals {damage} damage to nearby enemies and knocks them away.

ability5.name: Wind Bomb
ability5.description: Throw a wind bomb to target location. The impact pulls nearby enemies to the center and creates a {2}Wind Stream{-} that lasts for {areaduration}. Allies entering the wind stream gain {2}Haste{-} for {hasteduration}.

ability6.name: Tornado
ability6.description: Target ally is swept up into the air and becomes unhittable. They are tossed out of the tornado in their aim direction when the effect ends.

ability7.name: Companion Call
ability7.description: Your mount rushes to you from target location, dealing {damage} damage to enemies in its path. When it reaches you, you mount and gain a {2}Shield{-}. While shielded, you can't be dismounted and you can cast empowered {2}Razor Boomerangs{-}.

characters.name: Ulric
characters.description: Sworn protector of the weak, devout follower of the Way of Symphony, and unwavering light against the dark. Ulric, trained in the holy Monastery of Resonance, has spent many years traveling the lands to spread the word of the Light. He joins the Arena now to demonstrate to allies, foes, and onlookers alike the primacy of the True Path.

battlerites.name: Enchanted Weapon
battlerites.description: {2}Hammer of Justice{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage when affected by {2}Favor{-}.

battlerites.name: Cleave
battlerites.description: Charged {2}Hammer of Justice{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage. Deals {secondarydamage} damage and inflicts {2}Stun{-} on secondary targets.

battlerites.name: Devotion
battlerites.description: {2}Holy Light{-} healing increases by {healingbonus} when healing self or allies affected by {2}Favor{-}.

battlerites.name: Faith
battlerites.description: {2}Holy Light{-} recharges {rechargebonus} faster when {2}Smite{-} is active.

battlerites.name: Penitence
battlerites.description: {2}Intervene{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and reduces incoming healing by {healingreduction} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Divine Protection
battlerites.description: {2}Favor{-} reduces damage taken by {damagereduction}.

battlerites.name: Initiation
battlerites.description: {2}Intervene{-} travel distance increases by {distancefactor} when affected by {2}Favor{-}.

battlerites.name: Light Speed
battlerites.description: Absorbing an attack with {2}Radiant Shield{-} increases your movement speed by {hastefactor} for {duration}. Stacks up to {stacks} times.

battlerites.name: Halo
battlerites.description: Activating {2}Smite{-} grants a {2}Shield{-}. It absorbs up to {damageabsorb} damage for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Holy Fire
battlerites.description: The third {2}Smite{-} attack deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and explodes upon impact dealing {areadamage} area damage to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Holy Shackles
battlerites.description: {2}Smite{-} projectiles inflict a {slowfactor} {2}Snare{-} for {slowduration}.

battlerites.name: Vindicator
battlerites.description: {2}Condemn{-} cooldown is reduced by {cooldownreduction} and hits refresh the cooldown of {2}Intervene{-}.

battlerites.name: Godlike
battlerites.description: All effects of {2}Divinity{-} are doubled.

battlerites.name: Light's Embrace
battlerites.description: Blocking an attack with {2}Radiant Shield{-} sends out a wave of light, healing nearby allies for {healing} health.

ability1.name: Hammer of Justice
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals {damage} damage. Your weapon charges over time. When fully charged, it deals {bonusdamage} damage and inflicts {2}Stun{-} to closest enemy and {areadamage} area damage to nearby enemies.

ability2.name: Holy Light
ability2.description: Call down a beam of holy light that heals the ally nearest target location for {healing} health.

ability3.name: Intervene
ability3.description: Become immaterial and dash forward to slam an enemy dealing {damage} damage. Dashing through an ally heals self and ally for {healing} health, applies {2}Favor{-}, recharges your weapon and resets cooldown. Cannot hit allies affected by {2}Favor{-}.

ability4.name: Radiant Shield
ability4.description: Put up your shield and absorb projectile and melee attacks in front of you. Absorbing an attack charges your shield up to {count} times. Fires a wave of light in a cone dealing {damage} damage and inflicting {2}Blind{-} when the effect ends if your shield is charged. Each charge increases the radius.

ability5.name: Smite
ability5.description: Knock nearby enemies back and replace {2}Holy Light{-} with {2}Smite{-}, a projectile attack dealing {damage1} / {damage2} / {damage3} damage. The effect lasts for {charges} attacks or up to {duration}. The effect can be canceled by recasting the ability.

ability6.name: Condemn
ability6.description: Jump into the air and slam your hammer into the ground to send out a shockwave. The shockwave deals {damage} damage and launches an enemy into the air for {stunduration}.

ability7.name: Aegis of Valor
ability7.description: Throw your returning Aegis. Deals {mindamage}-{maxdamage} damage and inflicts {2}Incapacitate{-}, damage increases with travel distance. The Aegis lands on the ground on impact. Picking it up or catching it when it returns applies {2}Divinity{-}.

characters.name: Poloma
characters.description: Poloma uses shamanic powers to guide life and spirits alongside her protector and loyal creature, Toki. A dark disturbance among souls has put Poloma on a new path, leaving her safety and home behind. Driven by her burning curiosity and extraordinary senses, Poloma now seeks her answers in the arena.

battlerites.name: Specter
battlerites.description: {2}Other Side{-} causes your ally to become invisible for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Spirit Walker
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Other Side{-} movement speed bonus from {oldhastefactor} to {newhastefactor} and duration by {bonusduration}.

battlerites.name: Into the Realm
battlerites.description: {2}Other Side{-} heals {healing} bonus healing. Also reduces cooldown of {2}Other Side{-} by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Soul Theft
battlerites.description: Moving through an enemy during {2}Other Side{-} deals {damage} damage and heals you for {healing} health.

battlerites.name: Vengeful Spirit
battlerites.description: Teleporting to {2}Spirit Guide{-} resets the cooldown of {2}Spirit Rift{-}.

battlerites.name: Phantasm
battlerites.description: Ally affected by ^2Spirit Guide^- takes {damagereduction} less damage and enemy affected by ^2Spirit Guide^- takes {damageincrease} more damage.

battlerites.name: Ghostly Strike
battlerites.description: {2}Spirit Guide{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and knockback force increases by {knockbackbonus}.

battlerites.name: Spiritual Wind
battlerites.description: {2}Spirit Rift{-} increases your movement speed by {hastefactor} for {duration} when it inflicts {2}Spell Block{-}.

battlerites.name: Soul Essence
battlerites.description: Reduces cooldown of {2}Spirit Rift{-} by {cooldownreduction}. {2}Spell Block{-} interrupts further reduce cooldown by {cooldownreduction2}.

battlerites.name: Silver Fang
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Ghost Wolf{-} range by {range}. The first hit deals {damage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Dire Wolf
battlerites.description: The first {2}Ghost Wolf{-} hit inflicts {2}Root{-} for {immobilizeduration}.

battlerites.name: Affection
battlerites.description: {2}Ghost Wolf{-} returns to you afterward, granting you {energygain} energy and healing you for {healing} health.

battlerites.name: Pixie Dust
battlerites.description: {2}Pixie{-} deals full damage and healing on mimicked {2}Soul Bolts{-} and cooldown reduces by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Shimmering Bond
battlerites.description: Increases healing shared by {2}Spirit Link{-} from {oldsharefactor} to {newsharefactor}.

battlerites.name: Dark Souls
battlerites.description: Increases damage dealt by {2}Soul Bind{-} from {olddamagesharefactor} to {newdamagesharefactor} and range of {2}Soul Bind{-} by {bonusradius}.

battlerites.name: Equilibrium
battlerites.description: The first impact of ^2Ancestral Spirit^- applies ^2Spirit Link^- on allies and ^2Soul Bind^- on enemies.

battlerites.name: Condemn
battlerites.description: The second impact of {2}Ancestral Spirit{-} inflicts {2}Stun{-} for {stunduration}.

ability1.name: Soul Bolt
ability1.description: Fire a soul bolt that deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Soul Bind{-} on enemy hit. Heals {healing} health and applies {2}Spirit Link{-} on you and ally hit.

ability2.name: Other Side
ability2.description: Send target ally into the spirit realm, increasing their movement speed by {hastefactor} and making them immaterial but unable to use abilities. Heals nearby allies for {healing} health when the effect ends.

ability3.name: Spirit Guide
ability3.description: Project a spirit guide that heals an ally for {healing} health or deals {damage} damage and knocks an enemy back. Can be recast to teleport to the spirit.

ability4.name: Spirit Rift
ability4.description: Open a rift, inflicting {2}Spell Block{-} to nearby enemies. When {2}Spell Block{-} interrupts an ability, it inflicts {2}Panic{-}.

ability5.name: Ghost Wolf
ability5.description: Send out a ghost wolf that deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Soul Bind{-}. It bounces to a nearby enemy after each hit, up to {bounces} total hits.

ability6.name: Pixie
ability6.description: Summon a pixie that follows you and mimics your {2}Soul Bolt{-} casts. Mimicked {2}Soul Bolts{-} deal reduced damage and healing.

ability7.name: Ancestral Spirit
ability7.description: Summon an ancestral spirit at target location and become immaterial for {predelay}. Deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Fading Snare{-} to enemies and heals allies for {healing} health. After {delay}, the spirit departs to deal {enddamage} damage to enemies and heal allies for {endhealing} health.

characters.name: Croak
characters.description: His background is shrouded in mystery, his movements are supernatural and his reputation is whispered about. Croak loves to surprise his enemies, using his mobility to move in and out. His chameleonic stealth and flexible fighting style makes him exceptionally hard to catch.

battlerites.name: Mending Toxin
battlerites.description: Increases healing effect of {2}Toxin{-} from {originalhealing} to {newhealing}.

battlerites.name: Spit Spit Spit
battlerites.description: {2}Toxin Muck{-} gains {charges} ability charge but increases its cooldown by {cooldownincrease}.

battlerites.name: Triple Strike
battlerites.description: {2}Frog Leap{-} causes your next {hits} {2}Blade Flurry{-} attacks to deal {damage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Jungle Toad
battlerites.description: {2}Frog Leap{-} hits heal you for {healing} health.

battlerites.name: Venom Strike
battlerites.description: Using {2}Blade Flurry{-} during {2}Camouflage{-} inflicts venom that explodes after {delay}, dealing {damage} damage to nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Cut to the Chase
battlerites.description: Increases invisibility duration of {2}Camouflage{-} by {bonusduration}.

battlerites.name: Noxious Reaction
battlerites.description: {2}Noxious Lunge{-} inflicts {2}Root{-} for {immobilizeduration} and reapplies {2}Toxin{-}.

battlerites.name: Trickery
battlerites.description: {2}Noxious Lunge{-} hits reduce {2}Camouflage{-} cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Frog Frenzy
battlerites.description: Activating {2}Toxin Blades{-} increases attack speed of your next {ticks} {2}Blade Flurry{-} attacks. Also increases {2}Toxin Blades{-} bonus damage by {bonusdamage}.

battlerites.name: Momentum
battlerites.description: {2}Venom Wind{-} increases your movement speed by {hastefactor} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Lethal Toxins
battlerites.description: {2}Toxin{-} deals {tickdamage} bonus damage and reduces target's movement speed by {slowfactor}.

battlerites.name: Time to Strike
battlerites.description: Increases {2} Fading Haste{-} factor of {2}Camouflage{-} from {hastefactor1} to {hastefactor2} and haste duration from {hasteduration1} to {hasteduration2}.

battlerites.name: Slippery Skin
battlerites.description: Reduces damage taken by {damagereduction} for {duration} after {2}Camouflage{-} ends.

battlerites.name: Frog Slice
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Noxious Lunge{-} range by {rangeincrease}. It deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

ability1.name: Blade Flurry
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals {damage1} damage. {2}Frog Leap{-} and {2}Camouflage{-} increase the attack speed of {2}Blade Flurry{-} for the next {maxcharges} attacks.

ability2.name: Toxin Muck
ability2.description: Spit toxin muck at target location. Deals {damage} damage, inflicts {2}Toxin{-} and heals you for {healing} health on hit.

ability3.name: Frog Leap
ability3.description: Leap to target location and strike with your blades, dealing {damage} damage. Can be recast to leap again.

ability4.name: Camouflage
ability4.description: Become invisible, remove negative effects and gain {2}Fading Haste{-}. Using {2}Blade Flurry{-} while invisible inflicts {2}Stun{-}. Using other attacks ends this effect.

ability5.name: Noxious Lunge
ability5.description: Dash forward, piercing through enemies to deal {damage} damage.

ability6.name: Toxin Blades
ability6.description: Coat your blades in toxin, causing your {2}Blade Flurry{-} attacks to deal {bonusdamage} bonus damage, inflict {2}Toxin{-} and heal you for {bonushealing} health on hit.

ability7.name: Venom Wind
ability7.description: Dash forward in the shape of a venomous wind, piercing through enemies to inflict {2}Venom{-}.

characters.name: Freya
characters.description: Once a tribe queen, now a fearless contender. Her titanic hammers and overwhelming power of lightning is the perfect recipe for destruction.

battlerites.name: Static Hammers
battlerites.description: {2}Bash{-} hits on enemies already affected by {2}Static{-} increases the duration by {bonusduration}, up to a maximum duration of {maxduration}.

battlerites.name: Twin Hammers
battlerites.description: {2}Storm Mace{-} gains {amount} ability charge but increases its cooldown by {increasedcooldown}.

battlerites.name: Thunderbolt
battlerites.description: {2}Storm Mace{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage to enemies already affected by {2}Static{-} and {2}Incapacitate{-} duration increases by {duration}.

battlerites.name: Tempest
battlerites.description: {2}Storm Mace{-} hits increase your movement speed by {hastefactor} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Thundering Spring
battlerites.description: {2}Spring{-} range increases by {1}25{-} and movement speed bonus duration increases by {bonusduration}.

battlerites.name: Lightning Speed
battlerites.description: {2}Spring{-} increases your {2}Bash{-} attack speed by {attackspeedfactor} for the next {hits} attacks.

battlerites.name: Electric Conduction
battlerites.description: {2}Spring{-} causes your next {2}Bash{-} to grant you a {2}Shield{-}. It absorbs up to {shieldamount} damage for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Overcharge
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with {2}Electric Shield{-} inflicts {2}Static{-} on nearby enemies and grants other nearby allies a {2}Shield{-}. It absorbs up to {shieldvalue} damage for {shieldduration}.

battlerites.name: Hammer Time
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with {2}Electric Shield{-} reduces {2}Thunderclap{-} cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Torrent
battlerites.description: {2}Thunderclap{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and pulls enemies towards you.

battlerites.name: Rolling Thunder
battlerites.description: Move forward during {2}Thunderclap{-}.

battlerites.name: Surge
