battlerites.description: Reduces cooldown of {2}Charged Strike{-} by {cooldownreduction}. Hitting at least one enemy grants {energyreturn} energy.

battlerites.name: Thunderstruck
battlerites.description: {2}Lightning Strike{-} inflicts {2}Stun{-} for {stunduration}.

battlerites.name: Positive Charge
battlerites.description: Increases your damage output by {damagefractor} while you have an active {2}Electric Shield{-}.

battlerites.name: Lightning Rod
battlerites.description: Each enemy hit by {2}Thunderclap{-} grants you {2}Shield{-} that absorbs up to {shieldvalue} damage for {shieldduration}.

ability1.name: Bash
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals {damage1} / {damage2} / {damage3} damage. Deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage if enemy is affected by {2}Static{-}.

ability2.name: Storm Mace
ability2.description: Throw a mace that deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Static{-}. Consumes {2}Static{-} instead if the enemy is already affected by {2}Static{-}, knocking them back and inflicting {2}Incapacitate{-} if knocked into a wall.

ability3.name: Spring
ability3.description: Leap to target location and gain {2}Spring{-}.

ability4.name: Electric Shield
ability4.description: Counter incoming melee and projectile attacks. Countering any attack pulls that enemy towards you and inflicts {2}Static{-}. Grants you a {2}Shield{-} when you counter the first attack.

ability5.name: Thunderclap
ability5.description: Jump into the air, then slam your maces into the ground. Deals {damage} damage to nearby enemies and inflicts {2}Static{-}. Deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage to enemies already affected by {2}Static{-}.

ability6.name: Charged Strike
ability6.description: Cleaving melee attack that deals {damage} damage and grants a {2}Shield{-} for each hit. Consumes {2}Static{-} from enemies to increase the value of the {2}Shield{-}.

ability7.name: Lightning Strike
ability7.description: Leap high into the air, then strike down at target location. Deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Static{-}. Deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage to enemies already affected by {2}Static{-}.

characters.name: Jumong
characters.description: Jumong is a trophy collector who has wandered the wildlands in the pursuit of a worthy challenge. No longer being content with hunting the great beasts of the world has led him to enter the arena, looking for a new type of prey. He traps his foes and ends them with a well placed shot from his mighty bow.

battlerites.name: Perfect Shot
battlerites.description: {2}Steady Shot{-} inflicts {2}Stun{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Power Shot
battlerites.description: {2}Steady Shot{-} deals {damage} bonus damage and knocks the enemy back.

battlerites.name: Prey Drive
battlerites.description: {2}Steady Shot{-} hits heal you for {healing} health, and an additional {bonushealing} bonus health when consuming {2}Seeker's Mark{-}.

battlerites.name: Viper
battlerites.description: {2}Black Arrow{-} grants {speedmodifier} {2}Fading Haste{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Precision
battlerites.description: {2}Black Arrow{-} deals {damage} bonus damage and grants {energy} bonus energy.

battlerites.name: Marksman
battlerites.description: {2}Black Arrow{-} hits grant {charges} weapon charges.

battlerites.name: Crippling Hail
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Snare{-} factor of {2}Rain of Arrows{-} from {oldfactor} to {newfactor}.

battlerites.name: Arrow Storm
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Rain of Arrows{-} radius by {radiusincrease}. It deals {damage} bonus damage over the duration.

battlerites.name: Deadly Trap
battlerites.description: Your projectiles deal {damage} bonus damage to enemies caught in {2}Bear Trap{-}.

battlerites.name: Trapper
battlerites.description: {2}Bear Trap{-} lays down an additional trap in front of the first one that lasts for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Disabling Trap
battlerites.description: Enemies caught in {2}Bear Trap{-} deal {factor} reduced damage and receive {factor} less healing.

battlerites.name: Marked Prey
battlerites.description: {2}Bear Trap{-} inflicts {2}Seeker's Mark{-}.

battlerites.name: Panther
battlerites.description: Increases duration of {2}Prowl{-} by {duration} and reduces its cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Deadeye
battlerites.description: {2}Dragon Slayer{-} deals {mindamage} - {maxdamage} bonus damage based on charge-up duration.

battlerites.name: Death Mark
battlerites.description: Consuming ^2Seekers Mark^- deals {damage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Agility
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed by {hastemodifier}.

ability1.name: Hunting Arrow
ability1.description: Fire an arrow that deals {damage} damage and charges your bow on hit. A fully charged bow enables you to recast {2}Steady Shot{-}, {2}Black Arrow{-} or {2}Rain of Arrows{-}.

ability2.name: Steady Shot
ability2.description: Fire a powerful arrow that deals {damage} damage.

ability3.name: Black Arrow
ability3.description: Dash towards your move direction and fire an arrow that deals {damage} damage.

ability4.name: Rain of Arrows
ability4.description: Fire arrows that rain down at target location. It deals {damage} damage over {duration} and inflicts {2}Snare{-}. The first salvo also inflicts {2}Seeker's Mark{-}.

ability5.name: Bear Trap
ability5.description: Place a trap at target location. When the trap is triggered, it inflicts {2}Root{-} on nearby enemies.

ability6.name: Prowl
ability6.description: Become immaterial and movement speed increases by {hastefactor}. Removes movement impairing effects. Running into an enemy inflicts {2}Seeker's Mark{-}.

ability7.name: Dragon Slayer
ability7.description: Hold to charge an arrow to increase its damage and range. The arrow deals {damage} damage and pulls the enemy with it. Pulling them into another enemy or wall deals {targetdamage} damage to the second enemy and inflicts {2}Stuns{-} to both enemies.

characters.name: Shifu
characters.description: Expert in the martial art of Ni'Shu and master of the spear. A highly mobile and dangerous duelist. His extraordinary combat prowess culminates in a range of deadly melee attacks. Facing Shifu is like walking into a tornado of spearheads.

battlerites.name: Thrust
battlerites.description: {2}Impale{-} deals {damage} bonus damage and an additional {bonusdamagepercharge} bonus damage per weapon charge.

battlerites.name: Spear Lunge
battlerites.description: Increases lunge distance of {2}Impale{-} by {rangeincrease}.

battlerites.name: Ceremonial Spear
battlerites.description: {2}Impale{-} heals you for {bonushealing} health and {bonushealingpercharge} additional health per weapon charge.

battlerites.name: The Spear is the Way
battlerites.description: During {2}Fleetfoot{-}, {2}Spear Slash{-} hits grant {bonusenergy} bonus energy.

battlerites.name: Meditation
battlerites.description: Activating {2}Fleetfoot{-} near an ally heals you and your ally for {healing} health each.

battlerites.name: Swift Feet
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Fleetfoot{-} movement speed bonus from {hastefactor2} to {hastefactor1} and haste duration by {duration}.

battlerites.name: Poised to Strike
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with {2}Kunju{-} causes your next {2}Spear Slash{-} to deal {damage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Mantra
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with {2}Kunju{-} causes your next {2}Spear Slash{-} hit to heal you for {selfheal} health.

battlerites.name: Spear Slinger
battlerites.description: Hitting a wall with {2}Javelin{-} allows you to recast {2}Javelin{-} for {recastduration}. Also reduces its cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Javelin Master
battlerites.description: {2}Javelin{-} deals {damage} bonus damage. Also increases its range by {rangefactor}.

battlerites.name: Dirty Tricks
battlerites.description: {2}Javelin{-} inflicts {2}Root{-} for {immobilizeduration}.

battlerites.name: Whirling Blade
battlerites.description: {2}Tendon Swing{-} deals {damage} bonus damage and grants {energyreturn} energy when hitting at least one enemy.

battlerites.name: Spear Dance
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Whirlwind{-} movement speed bonus from {movementmodifier1} to {movementmodifier2}.

battlerites.name: Ferocious Stance
battlerites.description: Increases your maximum weapon charges by {ragebonus} and countering an attack with {2}Kunju{-} grants {weaponcharge} weapon charge.

ability1.name: Spear Slash
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals {damage1} damage. Successful hits charge your weapon, increasing the damage of your next {2}Impale{-}.

ability2.name: Impale
ability2.description: Lunge forward and thrust your spear in a line, piercing enemies to deal {damage} damage. Deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage per weapon charge.

ability3.name: Fleetfoot
ability3.description: You become immaterial and remove negative effects. Your movement speed increases by {speedpercent} and damage dealt reduces by {damagereduction} for the duration.

ability4.name: Kunju
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, teleport behind your enemy, heal yourself for {kunjuhealing} health, become immaterial for {immaterialduration}, and gain {2}Readiness{-}.

ability5.name: Javelin
ability5.description: Throw a javelin that deals {damage} damage and leap towards the enemy hit. Javelin can be used to pull yourself to a wall.

ability6.name: Tendon Swing
ability6.description: Swing your spear in a cleaving arc to deal {damage} damage and inflict {2}Incapacitate{-}.

ability7.name: Whirlwind
ability7.description: Spin into a whirlwind dance and deal {damage} damage over {duration} to nearby enemies. Grants you a {2}Shield{-} and movement speed increase for the duration.

characters.name: Jamila
characters.description: A young assassin from the Shadowblade clan, Jamila suddenly found herself the new leader after the death of her mother, the previous matriarch. As the youngest leader in the clan’s history, some call her too inexperienced and undeserving of the title. Determined to silence those detractors, Jamila enters the arena to prove her mastery of the Shadow Arts.

battlerites.name: Go for the Throat
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Stun{-} duration of {2}Deadly Blow{-} by {bonusduration} and reduces its cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Deadly Star
battlerites.description: {2}Shuriken{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage on each hit.

battlerites.name: Blade Swirl
battlerites.description: Countering an attack with {2}Shadow Dance{-} causes you to attack all nearby enemies, dealing {damage} damage and inflicting {2}Fading Snare{-} for {snareduration}.

battlerites.name: Quick Strike
battlerites.description: Hitting a wall with {2}Hook Shot{-} allows you to recast to perform a short dash strike, dealing {damage} piercing damage.

battlerites.name: Agile Shadow
battlerites.description: Allows you to cast {2}Elusive Strike{-} while in stealth, increasing stealth duration by {bonusduration}. You are revealed while traveling and re-enter stealth afterward.

battlerites.name: Taste of Blood
battlerites.description: {2}Shuriken{-} returns to you afterward, healing you for {healing} health based on enemies hit.

battlerites.name: Drawing Blood
battlerites.description: {2}Shadow Slice{-} heals you for {healing} health.

battlerites.name: Cripple
battlerites.description: {2}Elusive Strike{-} inflicts {2}Fading Snare{-} for {duration} and {2}Incapacitate{-} duration increases by {bonusduration}.

battlerites.name: Push Off
battlerites.description: Increases the max range of {2}Elusive Strike{-} by {rangebonus}.

battlerites.name: Deep Wounds
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Snare{-} duration of {2}Shuriken{-} by {bonusduration}.

battlerites.name: Phantom Blades
battlerites.description: {2}Phantom Cut{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Firing Mechanism
battlerites.description: Increases the range of {2}Hook Shot{-} by {3}15{-} and reduces its cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Momentum Strike
battlerites.description: {2}Hook Shot{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and inflicts {2}Root{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Lurking Phantom
battlerites.description: Hitting a wall with {2}Stalking Phantom{-}'s initial dash triggers a wall jump that inflicts {2}Incapacitate{-}.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by {energyfactor} and maximum energy by {energybonus}.

battlerites.name: Roundhouse Kick
battlerites.description: {2}Elusive Strike{-} can be recast to kick an enemy, dealing {damage} damage and knocking them away.

ability1.name: Assassin's Cut
ability1.description: Three quick stabs that deal {damage} damage each, followed by a heavy strike that deals {heavydamage} damage.

ability2.name: Shuriken
ability2.description: Throw a bouncing shuriken, dealing {damagelist} damage and inflicting {2}Snare{-}.

ability3.name: Elusive Strike
ability3.description: Hold to charge a dash for up to {casttime} to increase damage and range. It deals {mindamage}-{maxdamage} damage and dashing in to a wall triggers a wall jump that inflicts {2}Incapacitate{-}.

ability4.name: Shadow Dance
ability4.description: Counter the next melee or projectile attack. When you counter an attack, gain {2}Immaterial{-} for {immaterialduration}, turn invisible and increase your movement speed by {speedfactor} for {invisduration}. Your next {2}Assassins Cut{-} while invisible becomes {2}Shadow Slice{-}, dealing {damage} damage and inflicting {2}Phantom Cut{-}.

ability5.name: Hook Shot
ability5.description: Launch a hook that deals {projectiledamage} damage and pulls you and the enemy together. You strike after colliding, dealing {dashdamage} damage. {2}Hook Shot{-} can be used to pull yourself to a wall.

ability6.name: Deadly Blow
ability6.description: Strike forward with both weapons. Deals {damage} damage, inflicts {2}Stun{-} and heals yourself for {healing} health on hit.

ability7.name: Stalking Phantom
ability7.description: Summon a phantom that dashes forward, dealing {dashdamage} damage and stopping behind the first enemy hit. Upon arrival, it chases and strikes enemies in bursts for {burstdamage} damage up to {attacks} times.

characters.name: Ezmo
characters.description: Ezmo is an aggressive spell caster who can move quickly across the arena. Aradu, a powerful warlock summoned and imprisoned Ezmo but Ezmo saw his opportunity to escape when the warlock became too engrossed in reading his tome. He sealed Aradu's soul and mind within it and has been carrying the tome ever since.

battlerites.name: Exhaust
battlerites.description: Hitting the same enemy with {number} consecutive {2}Arcane Fires{-} inflicts {2}Fading Snare{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Warlock's Grip
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Chaos Grip{-} range by {rangeincrease}.

battlerites.name: Disruption
battlerites.description: {2}Chaos Grip{-} inflicts {2}Silence{-} for {minduration} to {maxduration}, based on charge-up duration.

battlerites.name: Collapse
battlerites.description: {2}Chaos Grip{-} deals {mindamage} - {maxdamage} bonus damage, based on charge-up duration.

battlerites.name: Wreak Havoc
battlerites.description: {2}Displace{-} increases your {2}Arcane Fire{-} attack speed by {1}30{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Chaos Barrage
battlerites.description: {2}Displace{-} grants {weaponcharges} extra weapon charge.

battlerites.name: Whizz
battlerites.description: Using {2}Displace{-} grants {hastefactor} Fading Haste for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Feedback
battlerites.description: Recast {2}Arcane Barrier{-} to fire a projectile. It deals {damage} damage for each of your charges.

battlerites.name: Spell Eater
battlerites.description: Negating attacks with {2}Arcane Barrier{-} grants twice as many weapon charges. For each charge gained, heal yourself for {healing} health.

battlerites.name: Imp Rush
battlerites.description: {2}Arcane Barrier{-} increases your movement speed by {hastefactor}. Also reduces its cooldown by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Undermine
battlerites.description: {2}Shackle{-} inflicts {2}Weaken{-}, reducing target's damage and healing output by {healingfactor} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Face Melt
battlerites.description: ^2Arcane Fire^- deals {damage} bonus damage to enemies rooted by ^2Shackle^-.

battlerites.name: Bolted
battlerites.description: {2}Shackle{-} hits grant {charges} weapon charge and increase {2}Arcane Fire{-} range by {rangefactor} until the next reload.

battlerites.name: Tome Of Restoration
battlerites.description: {2}Tome of Destruction{-} leashes onto nearby allies, healing for {healing} health over the duration.

battlerites.name: Grimoire of Death
battlerites.description: Increases pull force of {2}Grimoire of Chaos{-} by {bonusforce}. It deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

ability1.name: Arcane Fire
ability1.description: Launch a bolt of arcane fire that deals {damage} damage.

ability2.name: Chaos Grip
ability2.description: Hold to charge a projectile for up to {maxchargeduration} to increase damage and range. It deals {damage} damage, knocks nearby enemies back and pulls enemies far away towards you.

ability3.name: Displace
ability3.description: Turn into arcane energy, travel to target location and reload {2}Arcane Fire{-}. Can be recast.

ability4.name: Arcane Barrier
ability4.description: Negate melee and projectile attacks in front of you. Negating attacks grants {2}Arcane Fire{-} charges. You gain {1}1{-} charge per {damage} damage absorbed or {1}1{-} charge for each non-damaging attack.

ability5.name: Shackle
ability5.description: Manifest shackles at target location, dealing {damage} damage and inflicting {2}Root{-} to enemies in the area.

ability6.name: Tome of Destruction
ability6.description: Summon the Tome of Destruction at target location. The tome mimics your {2}Arcane Fire{-} attacks.

ability7.name: Grimoire of Chaos
ability7.description: Throw the Grimoire of Chaos to target location. The power of the grimoire draws nearby enemies towards it. It explodes after {duration}, dealing {damage} damage.

characters.name: Raigon
characters.description: Raigon, formerly the crown prince of Quna, is a skilled melee fighter trained in two-handed swordsmanship and martial arts. He hopes to break the evil spell cast upon his father and return home. For now, the arena serves as a decent place to find work and set the wheels in motion for his retaliation.

battlerites.name: Overflowing Power
battlerites.description: Hitting at least one enemy with {2}Heavenly Strike{-} grants you a charge of {2}Slicing Winds{-}.

battlerites.name: Headlong Rush
battlerites.description: Increases dash length of {2}Retribution{-} by {lengthincrease}.

battlerites.name: Binding Light
battlerites.description: {2}Retribution{-} inflicts {2}Fading Snare{-} for {duration}. Increases duration by {bonusduration} per weapon charge.

battlerites.name: Royal Descent
battlerites.description: {2}Heavenly Strike{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and inflicts {2}Fading Snare{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Hawk Dive
battlerites.description: {2}Heavenly Strike{-} inflicts {weakenfactor} {2}Weaken{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Acrobatics
battlerites.description: Increases maximum range of {2}Heavenly Strike{-} by {1}30{-} and decreases minimum distance by {1}50{-}.

battlerites.name: Invigorate
battlerites.description: Move at {1}100{-} movement speed during {2}Parry{-}. Heal nearby allies for {healing} health when {2}Parry{-} ends.

battlerites.name: Riposte
battlerites.description: When {2}Parry{-} expires, perform a {2}Spinning Slash{-}. It deals {damage} damage and inflict {2}Stun{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Duelist
battlerites.description: Negating any attack with {2}Parry{-} heals you for {health} health. Negating the first attack grants you a charge of {2}Slicing Winds{-}.

battlerites.name: Aerial Strike
battlerites.description: {2}Seismic Shock{-} can be recast to leap to the airborne enemy and strike them, dealing {damage} damage and increasing air duration by {duration}.

battlerites.name: Perilous Height
battlerites.description: {2}Seismic Shock{-} deals {targetdamage} bonus damage upon landing and deals {areadamage} damage to other nearby enemies.

battlerites.name: Soaring Speed
battlerites.description: {2}Seismic Shock{-} hits grant you {factor} {2}Fading Haste{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Dragon Mastery
battlerites.description: {2}Dragon Palm{-} hits allow you to recast it for {recastduration}.

battlerites.name: The Tiger and the Dragon
battlerites.description: {2}Wrath of the Tiger{-} ends with a {2}Heavenly Strike{-}.

battlerites.name: Agility
battlerites.description: Increases movement speed by {hastemodifier}.

ability1.name: Sword Slash
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals {damage} damage. Successful hits reduce cooldown of {2}Retribution{-} by {cooldownreduction} and charge your weapon, increasing the power of your next {2}Retribution{-}.

ability2.name: Retribution
ability2.description: Dash forward and cleave nearby enemies to deal {damage} damage and heal yourself for {healing} health on hit. Deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and heals yourself for {bonushealing} bonus health on hit per weapon charge.

ability3.name: Heavenly Strike
ability3.description: Leap to target location and strike with your sword. Deals {damage} damage to enemies in front of you.

ability4.name: Parry
ability4.description: Negate up to {reflects} melee and projectile attacks. Melee attacks trigger {2}Counterattacks{-} that inflict {2}Stun{-} and projectiles are redirected at your aim direction.

ability5.name: Seismic Shock
ability5.description: Send forth a seismic shock, dealing {damage} damage to the first enemy hit and launching them into the air for {stunduration}.

ability6.name: Dragon Palm
ability6.description: Dash forward and strike to deal {damage} damage, inflict {2}Fading Snare{-} and knock the enemy back. Knocking an enemy into a wall deals {extradamage} bonus damage.

ability7.name: Wrath of the Tiger
ability7.description: Dash forward and strike to deal {damage} damage. Upon hit, bounce between nearby enemies and strike them, dealing {tickdamage} damage over {duration}. Afterward, dash towards your aim direction. Recast to end this effect early.

characters.name: Thorn
characters.description: Ancient folklore speaks of Thorn, the destructive apparition. Using its network of thorn-covered roots, it would whip, rupture and drain the life out of any living thing indiscriminately. Some say Thorn is just a story to keep kids out of the forests at night, others say it is an old lie used as a cover-up for misdeeds. Thorn’s presence in the Arena is both a mystery, and a very bad omen.

battlerites.name: Whiplash
battlerites.description: {2}Evil Clutch{-} hits allow you to recast to strike nearby enemies, dealing {damage} damage and inflicting {2}Thorns{-}.

battlerites.name: Deep Burrow
battlerites.description: {2}Burrow{-} causes you to become invisible for the duration.

battlerites.name: Lurker
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Burrow{-} duration by {durationincrease}.

battlerites.name: Impaling Roots
battlerites.description: Moving under an enemy during {2}Burrow{-} sends impaling roots upwards, dealing {damage} damage to the enemy after a {impactdelay} delay.

battlerites.name: Neurotoxin
battlerites.description: {2}Thorns{-} reduces target's damage and healing output by {weakenfactor} for {weakenduration}.

battlerites.name: Hamstring Briars
battlerites.description: {2}Thorns{-} reduces target's movement speed by {slowfactor}.

battlerites.name: Parasitic Stems
battlerites.description: {2}Thorns{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and heals you for {bonushealing} bonus health over its duration.

battlerites.name: Sinister Sap
battlerites.description: {2}Entangle{-} deals {damage} damage over its duration. Reduces cooldown of {2}Entangling Roots{-} by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Critical Backlash
battlerites.description: Each stinging volley inflicts {2}Thorns{-} on nearby enemies. Reduces cooldown of {2}Barbed Husk{-} by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: Regrowth
battlerites.description: {2}Root Claw{-} and {2}Root Grip{-} hits reduce incoming damage by {damagereduction} for {duration}. Stacks up to {maxstacks} times.

battlerites.name: No Escape
battlerites.description: {2}Burrow{-} underground at the end of {2}Dead Roots{-}. The {2}Burrow{-} lasts for up to {duration}.

battlerites.name: Creeping Roots
battlerites.description: {2}Entangle{-} spreads towards nearby enemies when the effect is broken, dealing {damage} damage to enemies and inflicting {2}Lesser Entangle{-}.

battlerites.name: Fearsome Uprootal
battlerites.description: Each enemy hit by {2}Burrow{-} grants you a {2}Shield{-} that absorbs up to {shieldvalue} damage for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Grounding Grasp
battlerites.description: {2}Evil Clutch{-} inflicts {2}Root{-} for {silenceduration}.

battlerites.name: Branch Out
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Root Grip{-} range by {rangeincrease}. {2}Root Grip{-} pulls enemies closer and deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

ability1.name: Root Claw
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals {damagelist} damage. Every third attack is a {2}Root Grip{-} that heals you for {healing} health on hit and pulls enemies closer.

ability2.name: Leeching Thorns
ability2.description: Launch {amount} leeching thorns. Each projectile deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Thorns{-}.

ability3.name: Burrow
ability3.description: Burrow underground, increasing movement speed by {hastefactor} and removing movement impairing effects. Emerge from below after the duration, dealing {damage} damage and inflicting {2}Stun{-} to nearby enemies. Recast to emerge early.

ability4.name: Evil Clutch
ability4.description: Grow roots from the ground and pull them towards you, dragging along any enemies in their path and dealing {damage} damage.

ability5.name: Entangling Roots
ability5.description: Send whirling roots forward that deal {damage} damage and inflict {2}Entangle{-}.

ability6.name: Barbed Husk
ability6.description: Grant a {2}Shield{-} to target ally, making them immune to disables. Melee and projectile attacks absorbed by {2}Barbed Husk{-} trigger a stinging volley that deals {damage} damage to nearby enemies. While shielded, the target is unable to move or use abilities.

ability7.name: Dead Roots
ability7.description: Burrow and travel to target location, dealing {impactdamage} damage in a path and leaving a trail of dead roots behind you. The roots block projectiles, inflict {2}Snare{-} and deal {damage} damage over {areaduration}.

characters.name: Bakko
characters.description: Bakko has a proud history as a heroic brawler, armed with both axe and shield. He uses his shield to protect teammates and outmaneuver enemies. Watch out for his earth-shattering dash attacks, as even calm warriors sometimes go berserk.

battlerites.name: Axe and Shield
battlerites.description: {2}War Axe{-} hits reduce the cooldown of {2}Bulwark{-} by {cooldownreduction}.

battlerites.name: The Red Axe
battlerites.description: {2}Blood Axe{-} hits heal you for {healing} health plus {bonushealing} additional health per weapon charge.

battlerites.name: Howling Axes
battlerites.description: {2}Blood Axe{-} hits reduce its cooldown by {reduction}.

battlerites.name: Hamstring
battlerites.description: {2}Blood Axe{-} inflicts {2}Fading Snare{-} for {gradualslowduration}.

battlerites.name: Warlord's Axe
battlerites.description: {2}Blood Axe{-} deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage and an additional {bonusdamagepercharge} bonus damage per weapon charge.

battlerites.name: Adrenaline Rush
battlerites.description: {2}Valiant Leap{-} causes your next {2}War Axe{-} hit to deal {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Bravery
battlerites.description: {2}Valiant Leap{-} grants {damagereduction} damage reduction for {duration} to nearby allies.

battlerites.name: Heroic Leap
battlerites.description: Increases max range of {2}Valiant Leap{-} by {1}20{-}. It deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Shield Bash
battlerites.description: {2}Bulwark{-} can be recast to use {2}Shield Bash{-}. It deals {damage} damage and inflicts {factor} {2}Weaken{-} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Mobile Defence
battlerites.description: ^2Bulwark^- increases movement speed by {hastefactor}.

battlerites.name: Dizzying Dash
battlerites.description: {2}Shield Dash{-} inflicts {slowpercent} {2}Snare{-} for {slowduration}. Pushing an enemy into a wall deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Adrenaline Slam
battlerites.description: Hitting an enemy with {2}Shield Dash{-} causes your next {2}War Axe{-} hit to deal {bonusdamage} bonus damage.

battlerites.name: Raging Ram
battlerites.description: Increases range of {2}Shield Dash{-} by {1}25{-} and reduces cooldown by {reduction}.

battlerites.name: Rampage
battlerites.description: {2}War Shout{-} increases attack speed of {2}War Axe{-} and {2}Blood Axe{-} by {1}33{-} and movement speed by {factor} for {duration}.

battlerites.name: Mammoth Stomp
battlerites.description: Increases {2}Stun{-} duration of {2}Heroic Charge{-} by {duration}.

battlerites.name: Inspiration
battlerites.description: Increases energy gain from abilities by {energyfactor} and maximum energy by {energybonus}.

ability1.name: War Axe
ability1.description: Melee attack that deals {damage1} damage. Successful hits reduce cooldown of {2}Blood Axe{-} by {cooldownreduction} and charge your weapon, increasing the damage of your next {2}Blood Axe{-}.

ability2.name: Blood Axe
ability2.description: Throw an axe that deals {damage} damage. Deals {bonusdamage} bonus damage per weapon charge.

ability3.name: Valiant Leap
ability3.description: Leap into the air and strike down at target location, dealing {damage} damage to nearby enemies and inflicting {2}Snare{-}.

ability4.name: Bulwark
ability4.description: Put up your shield and block projectile and melee attacks in front of you. Reflects enemy projectiles and inflicts {2}Stun{-} on enemy melee attackers.

ability5.name: Shield Dash
ability5.description: Dash forward and grab an enemy, pushing them in front of you. Pushing them into a wall deals {damage} damage and inflicts {2}Stun{-}.

ability6.name: War Shout
ability6.description: Let loose a war shout that grants a {2}Shield{-} to nearby allies, absorbing up to {shieldvalue} damage for {duration}.

ability7.name: Heroic Charge
ability7.description: Rush forward and grab an enemy, dealing {damage} damage and pushing them in front of you. Deals {areadamage} area damage and inflicts {2}Stun{-} when reaching max range or colliding with a wall or another enemy.
